    {
      "lineNumber": 253132,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そういや何名かいたかな・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Come to think of it, were there several people...?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253133,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "よし、助けに行くぞ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Alright, let's go rescue them."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253134,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔物達が率いる荷馬車の一団を発見",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Discovered a caravan of wagons led by monsters."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253135,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "荷馬車１０台ほど、捕虜の人間（民間人）２００名ほどが引いている",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "About 10 wagons, pulling roughly 200 human prisoners (civilians)."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253136,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "周囲に魔物隊長と１００名ほどの魔物",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Around them, a monster commander and about 100 monsters."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253137,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス達に気が付くと魔物部隊が襲ってきた",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "When they noticed Rance and the others, the monster troops attacked."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253138,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "＞戦闘",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ">Battle"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253139,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔物部隊を倒す、捕虜の人間達は助かったーと喜びランス達に感謝",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Defeated the monster troops, the rescued human prisoners happily thanked Rance and the others."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253140,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "荷馬車の荷物に金目の物があるかみるが・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Checked the wagons' cargo for anything valuable, but..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253141,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ゴミのような食材、動物の死体、人間の死体、腐乱している物もある、臭い",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Trash-like ingredients, animal carcasses, human corpses, some rotten—very smelly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253142,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "これなんだ・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "What is this..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253143,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔人様の料理の材料らしいです。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Apparently these are ingredients for the Demon Lord's cooking."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253144,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "質とかどがいしでとにかく物量重視。大量です。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Quality doesn’t matter; it’s all about quantity. A huge amount."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253145,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "まぁ、いい・・それより、俺様がお前達を助けてやった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Well, whatever... More importantly, I saved you all."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253146,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "はい、ありがとうございますと村長みたいな男",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, thank you,\" said a man who looked like the village chief."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253147,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "どうやら、この捕虜達のまとめやくらしい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It seems he is the one in charge of these prisoners."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253148,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "助けてやった、さらにお前達を安全な所まで連れていってやろう",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I've saved you, and I’ll also take you to a safe place."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253149,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "だが、俺様は御褒美が欲しい　わかるな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But I want a reward. You understand that, right?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253150,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "女だ、美女をよこせ、ここに一人か二人はいるだろう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Women. Send me some beauties; there must be one or two here."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253151,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "捕虜達がざわざわと相談する・・困った事になったぞ、でも、せっかく助けてもらったのに逆らうのは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The prisoners murmured and consulted... This is troublesome, but they don't want to oppose us since we've saved them."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253152,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そうしているうちに、一人の女の子がかつぎだされる",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "While this was happening, a girl was carried forward."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253153,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "私、嫌だから・・ちょっとやめて、アナセルであった",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I don't want to... stop it,\" it was Ancerel."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253154,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "がははは、またお前か。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Gahaha, it's you again."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253155,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "感謝して俺に抱かれるがよい",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Be grateful and let me embrace you."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253156,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "エロシーン",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Erotic scene)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253157,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "だが、突っ込まれそうな所で、アナセルはランスを突き飛ばして逃げる",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But just when things were about to escalate, Ancerel shoved Rance away and ran off."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253158,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あっ、逃げた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Ah, she escaped."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253159,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "長老ぽい男、いかん　あっちは魔軍がいっぱいいる所だ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The man who looks like an elder said, 'No, over there is full of demon troops.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253160,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "しかたない、追いかけるか",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Can't be helped, we'll have to chase after her."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253161,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そしてアナセルに追いつく。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And then they caught up to Ancerel."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253162,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "どうしてこんなひどい事をするのよ、あんた悪い奴とかわらない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Why are you doing such awful things? You're no different from a bad person.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253163,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そうだよ、別に俺様は正義の味方では無い。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That's right. I'm not some hero of justice."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253164,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "お前は俺様がゲットした褒美なのだ、プレゼントがかってに逃げるな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You are the reward I claimed, so don't run away like some gift."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253165,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "エロシーン",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Erotic scene)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253166,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "今度は、ちゃんとセックスします。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "This time, we will have proper sex."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253167,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ふぅ、満足",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Phew, satisfied."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253168,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " "
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253169,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "村長に聞く、お前達は魔人バボラの餌の材料を届けさせてられていたんだな",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Asked the village chief, 'You people were forced to deliver the ingredients for the Demon Babora's food, right?'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253170,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "バボラの食事を作っている場所は分かるか",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Do you know where Babora's meals are prepared?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253171,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "はい、私達が行かされようとしていた所なので、この先のノシタタ村です。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, we were being taken there. It's Noshitata Village ahead.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253172,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "アナセルルートの場合",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In the case of Ancerel’s route"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253173,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ノシタタ村に到着した。こっそり様子をうかがう",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Arrived at Noshitata Village. Secretly observing the situation."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253174,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔物に占領された村、捕虜となった村人が働かされている",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The village is occupied by monsters; villagers imprisoned as slaves are made to work."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253175,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "直径１０メートルにおよぶ巨大な皿",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A gigantic plate about 10 meters in diameter."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253176,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そこに　汚いポテトサラダみたいなのがデンと積まれていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "On it was piled a large heap of something like dirty potato salad."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253177,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ネコ車などで村人が運んできて、どんどん盛りつけをしている",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Villagers brought it with wheelbarrows and kept heaping it on."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253178,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "急げー、そろそろバボラ様のお食事の時間だぞ。と魔物兵が命令している",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hurry up! It's almost time for Lord Babora's meal,\" ordered a monster soldier."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253179,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスがみんなに言う、よしあの皿の後ろに隠れるぞ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance said to everyone, 'Alright, hide behind that plate.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253180,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "皿に隠れている所、バボラの足音が聞こえて来た",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "While hiding behind the plate, they heard Babora’s footsteps approaching."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253181,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "どうするんですか？と聞かれる",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Someone asked, 'What do we do now?'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253182,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ふふふ、前に遠くから見て確認したのだ、あのデカブツし食事をする時、この皿を",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Heh heh heh, I checked from afar before — when that big guy eats, he brings this plate..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253183,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "顔の前にもってきて書き込むように飯を食うのを",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He holds it right in front of his face and devours the food like writing on paper."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253184,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "だから、この皿に隠れていたら、自動的に奴の顔の前に運んでくれるわけだ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "So if we hide in this plate, it'll be carried right in front of his face automatically."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253185,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そこで攻撃する",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Then we attack."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253186,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "・・・もし、すぐにかっこまれてたら、食事と一緒に食べられてしまうんじゃ？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...If we're immediately surrounded, won’t we be eaten along with the meal?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253187,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "はっ・・それは考えてなかった、やばいか・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hah... I hadn’t thought about that... Is that bad?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253188,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "・・・いや、食事の皿に異物がついてたらランスはどうする？　もろん放り投げるぞ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No... If there’s something strange in his meal, what would Rance do? Of course, he’d toss it away.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253189,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "はっ・・その場合もあるな、やばいかも・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hah... that could happen too. This might be bad..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253190,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "もう、無茶苦茶、どうなるのよ・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "This is a mess, what’s going to happen..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253191,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ん・・そうだな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hmm... yeah."
    }
  ]
}

